-- Criar registros de presença mock
INSERT INTO attendance (appointmentId, patientId, familyUserId, therapistUserId, therapyType, scheduledDate, status, markedByUserId, notes, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  a.id,
  a.patientId,
  1,
  a.therapistUserId,
  a.therapyType,
  a.startTime,
  'present',
  5,
  'Paciente chegou no horário',
  NOW(),
  NOW()
FROM appointments a
WHERE a.startTime < NOW()
LIMIT 3;
